    "Adapting the computations from [4, Proposition 2], we successively write∫ I h q-1 (t, w)∂ t h(t, w)dw = ∫ I h q-1 (t, w) ⎛ ⎝ σ 2 p + σ 2 ℓ 2 ∂ 2 w ((1 -w 2)h(t, w)) + ∂ w (λ p (ω p + ε) 2 (w -m w (t))h(t, w)) + ∂ w (λ ℓ (ω ℓ + ε)(w -µ ℓ)h(t, w)) ⎞ ⎠ dw = σ 2 p + σ 2 ℓ 2 ∫ I h q-1 (t, w)∂ w ((1 -w 2)∂ w h(t, w))dw + ∫ I h q-1 (t, w)∂ w (((λ p (ω p + ε) 2 + λ ℓ (ω ℓ + ε) -σ 2 p -σ 2 ℓ)w -(λ p m w (t) + λ ℓ µ ℓ))h(t, w))dw = T 1 + T 2,by performing one derivation in the diffusion term.",
